quran[12]{c,v,t}:
  42,52,"Wakathalika awhaynailayka roohan min amrina ma kunta tadree maalkitabu wala al-eemanu walakinjaAAalnahu nooran nahdee bihi man nashao min AAibadinawa-innaka latahdee ila siratin mustaqeem"
  42,53,"Sirati Allahi allatheelahu ma fee assamawati wamafee al-ardi ala ila Allahi taseerual-omoor"
  43,1,"Ha-meem"
  43,2,"Walkitabi almubeen"
  43,3,"Inna jaAAalnahu qur-ananAAarabiyyan laAAallakum taAAqiloona"
  43,4,"Wa-innahu fee ommi alkitabi ladaynalaAAaliyyun hakeem"
  43,5,"Afanadribu AAankumu aththikrasafhan an kuntum qawman musrifeen"
  43,6,"Wakam arsalna min nabiyyin feeal-awwaleen"
  43,7,"Wama ya/teehim min nabiyyin illakanoo bihi yastahzi-oon"
  43,8,"Faahlakna ashadda minhum batshanwamada mathalu al-awwaleen"
  43,9,"Wala-in saaltahum man khalaqa assamawatiwal-arda layaqoolunna khalaqahunna alAAazeezualAAaleem"
  43,10,"Allathee jaAAala lakumu al-ardamahdan wajaAAala lakum feeha subulan laAAallakum tahtadoon"
